\\n\\r\\n&lt;hr \\/&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p class=&quot;name&quot;&gt;Thank you, Mary for all of your help and support last week during the mentoring. Testimonial sent: The personal mentoring with John Person is by far the best trading training I have experienced in 20 years! John adapted the training to suit my personal requests, and he more than fulfilled my expectations. From learning about his proprietary indicators (and receiving &amp;hellip;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n\\r\\n&lt;hr \\/&gt;\\r\\n&lt;ul class=&quot;list&quot;&gt;\\r\\n&lt;\\/ul&gt;\\r\\n\\r\\n&lt;ul class=&quot;pagination&quot;&gt;\\r\\n&lt;\\/ul&gt;\\r\\n&lt;\\/div&gt;\\r\\n&lt;script&gt;\\r\\n      var monkeyList = new List(\'test-list\', {\\r\\n  valueNames: [\'name\'],\\r\\n  page: 18,\\r\\n  pagination: true\\r\\n});\\r\\n      &lt;\\/script&gt;\"}',	'0000-00-00',	'0000-00-00'),
