(412,	'course',	'Traders Mastering Course',	'traders-mastering-course',	'{\"featureImage\":\"assets\\/setting_header\\/vc_gitem_image2.png\",\"coursePrice\":\"$1498\",\"coursecat\":\"pro_trader\",\"buyNowUrl\":\"https:\\/\\/www.personsplanet.com\\/cmd.php?pid=eb266fb87276485290f40d3cf39d6858&bn=1\",\"courseFeature\":\"&lt;p&gt;This incredible training course will be the best trading System and method money can buy. As you may know, I am dedicated in helping brokers, floor traders and individual traders become the best traders possible. Reading books is a great way to learn but by watching and listening to spoken words and watching the instructions on a high resolution, professionally produced course, your learning curve will increase dramatically!&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n\\r\\n&lt;p&gt;I am dedicated to helping you win. That is why I am offering you my one of a kind &amp;ldquo;Advanced Candle Charting combined with Pivot Point Analysis&amp;rdquo;&amp;nbsp; trading course. There is no doubt it will enlighten and energize your trading! This is the essence of my work.&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n\\r\\n&lt;p&gt;I will show you how to put together a trading plan with amazing consistency that will help make you trade smarter, with less risk than you ever have before. Learn which candle pattern brings immediate results, learn the Pivot Point method and how to implement a moving average system that will help you narrow the playing field to select the next day, week or months: High , Low or both!&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n\\r\\n&lt;p&gt;I will show how to choose the right pivot points and teach you to devise your own setups, and triggers based on a moving average approach.&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n\\r\\n&lt;p&gt;My Promise to You&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n\\r\\n&lt;p&gt;I will give you the TOOLS designed to last you a lifetime. My goal is to help you get elevated into the top ranks of traders by using solid, historically valid methods all of which are specific, 100% objective, and straightforward. My promise to you is